quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  40,66,"Maaku: \"Min mi ha…óaama rewugol …óin …ói noddoton gaanin Allah, tuma nde …ďannganduyeeji …óin ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,67,"Ko Kanko woni tagu…óo on e mbumbuldi, refti e to…ď…ďere (maniiyu), refti e he…ó…óere, refti O yaltiniri on penuu…ďe fii no yottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayee…ďe, - no e mo'on, ∆īettitetee…ďe ado …óum, - haa no yottoron lajal happaangal, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  40,68,"Ko Kanko woni wuurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: \"Laato\", o laatoo"
  40,69,"E a tinaali, …ďen yeddondirtee…ďe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko honno …ďe firlitoraa"
  40,70,"∆Āen fennu…ďe Deftere nden, e kon ko Men nuliri Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen; …ďe aray anndude"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje …óen wa…óoyaa e daa…óe ma…ď…ďe, e jolokooje(callalle) …óen, hara hi…ďe daasiree"
  40,72,ka nder wul…óam; refti …ďe hu…ď…ďoyee ka nder Yiite
  40,73,"Refti …ďe wi'anee: \"Ko honto woni …óin …ói kafidayno…óon"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?\" ∆Āe wi'a: \"∆äi majjitike men. Wurin, men wonaano ko adii, e rewugol hay huunde\". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta heefer…ďe …ďen"
  40,75,"Ko wa…ói on …óum, ko ko weltorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko wewlirayno…óon kon"
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton. Nge bonii jaa∆īorde wonande mawnintinii…ďe …ďen"
  40,77,"Mu√Ī√Īo. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Men hollete yoga e ko Men fodi …ďe kon, maa hara Men ∆īettite (ado mun) ko ka Amen …ďe ruttirtee"
  40,78,"Gom…óii Men imminii Nulaa…ďe ado maa. Hino e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Men sifani maa fii mun; hino ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Men sifanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol Aaya, si wanaa e duŇčayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √Īaawirte meerente'en sooya nden √Īalnde"
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo On neemoraa…ói …óin ko wa…ó…óoron, √Īaamon kadi e majji"
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino woodani on e majji, e no yottoron e majji, haaju hittu…óo e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laa…óe …óen, woni ko ronndete…óon"
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji Makko …óin. Ko hon…óum e maandeeji Allah …óin, woni ko yeddoton"
  40,82,"E …ďee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe ndaara ko honno battane …ďeya ado ma…ď…ďe wattinirnoo? ∆Āen no …ďurunoo …ďe …óuude e sa…ótude doole e batteeji [wa…óaa…ói] ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ďe faggotonoo, duncanaano …ďe"
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addannoo…ďe …ďanngannduyeeji …óin, …ďe wewliri ganndal ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon. ∆Āe huu…ďitiraa kon ko …ďe jalkitaynoo"
  40,84,"Nde …ďe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"Men gom…óinii Allah tun, men yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e sirkannde"
  40,85,"Kono gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe wonaano ko nafata …ďe, fewndo …ďe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen; …óum ko laawol Allah non, gom…óii …óun yawtiino e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Yeddu…ďe …ďen sooyi …óon nden √Īalnde"
  41,1,"Haa, Miim"
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Yurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande Aayeeje mun, janngeteende e …óemngal aarabu, wonannde yim…ďe anndoo…ďe"
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jertina. Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, …óuurnii, …ďen …ďe nanataa"
  41,5,"∆Āe wi'i: \"∆Āer…óe amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mun kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi me…óen e golle amen"
  41,6,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko ne…ó…óanke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, wonnde Rewetee…óo mon on, ko Rewetee…óo gooto. √Ďii…ďee e …óum, insinano…óon Mo\". Bone woodanii sirkoo…ďe …ďen"
  41,7,"…ďe jonnataa …ďen zakka, hara kadi hi…ďe yeddi fii laakara"
  41,8,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa"